about.inbox.intro1: You’re now seeing the new inbox and profile in Altinn. These will gradually replace the current solutions. The goal is to make it easier for you to navigate, stay organized, and have better communication with the public sector.
about.inbox.intro2: The new inbox is part of
about.inbox.section.availability.link: the inbox you are familiar with.
about.inbox.section.availability.p1: The new solution is being rolled out gradually, so some messages or functions may be missing. Until everything is in place, you can still use the version of the inbox and profile you are familiar with.
about.inbox.section.availability.title: Still under development
about.inbox.section.dialogs.bullet1: See the status of a case and whether any action is required from you.
about.inbox.section.dialogs.bullet2: Easily view when a conversation was last updated and who has read it.
about.inbox.section.dialogs.bullet3: Move, sort, archive, or delete messages as you wish. If you delete a conversation by mistake, you can easily restore it.
about.inbox.section.dialogs.p1: Altinn brings together all your digital communication with the public sector. In the new inbox, related messages are grouped into a single conversation, giving you a clearer overview.
about.inbox.section.dialogs.title: What's new in your inbox
about.inbox.section.feedback.p1: We're continuously improving the inbox and profile, and we'd like to hear what you think. If you have questions or suggestions, please contact us at
about.inbox.section.feedback.title: We'd love your feedback
about.inbox.section.profile.bullet1: Get a clear overview of your personal details, favorites, and the organizations or associations you have access to.
about.inbox.section.profile.bullet2: Manage notification settings for all entities you have access to — all in one place.
about.inbox.section.profile.p1: The new profile makes it easier to find what you need and stay organized.
about.inbox.section.profile.title: What's new in your profile
